        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "# ex_gocd CI Pipeline Observability\n\nEvery pipeline trigger creates a correlated OTel trace: `pipeline.trigger` → `scheduler.enqueue` → `scheduler.assign_work` → `job.assign` → `job.status_update` → `job.complete`. Agents connecting produce `agent.connect` spans.\n\n**[Jaeger →](http://localhost:16686/search)** by `service=ex_gocd`  |  **[Logs →](/d/ci-logs)** Loki viewer  |  **[Analytics →](http://localhost:4000/analytics)** MTTR/pass-rate",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
