    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "id": 20,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "## Trace Structure (actual spans)\n\nEach pipeline trigger creates a single trace:\n\n```\nTrace ID: a1b2c3... (service: ex_gocd)\n│\n├── pipeline.trigger  [pipeline.name=demo, pipeline.counter=42]\n│   ├── scheduler.enqueue  [stage.name=build, job.name=compile]\n│   └── scheduler.assign_work  [agent.uuid=abc, pipeline.name=demo]\n│       └── job.assign  [agent.uuid=abc, job.instance_id=5]\n│           ├── job.status_update  [job.state=Building]\n│           ├── job.status_update  [job.state=Completing]\n│           └── job.status_update  [job.state=Completed, job.result=Passed]\n│               └── job.complete  [job.result=Passed, status=Ok]\n│\n├── agent.connect  [agent.uuid=abc, agent.hostname=worker-1]\n```\n\n**Span status**: `Ok` (green) = Passed; `Error` (red) = Failed/Cancelled.\n**Log correlation**: logs carry `trace_id` + `span_id` — click through from Jaeger to Loki.\n**Config**: `lib/ex_gocd/vsm_tracer.ex`, `lib/ex_gocd/logger_json.ex`, `otel/collector-config.yml`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Trace Structure",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "id": 21,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "## Attribute Reference\n\nAll spans use OpenTelemetry `dot.case` convention:\n\n| Attribute | Spans | Example |\n|---|---|---|\n| `pipeline.name` | all pipeline/job | `demo` |\n| `pipeline.counter` | all pipeline/job | `42` |\n| `stage.name` | scheduler + job | `build` |\n| `stage.counter` | scheduler + job | `1` |\n| `job.name` | all job spans | `compile` |\n| `job.instance_id` | job.assign, job.complete | `5` |\n| `job.state` | job.status_update | `Building` |\n| `job.result` | job.complete, job.status_update | `Passed` |\n| `agent.uuid` | agent + job spans | `abc123-def...` |\n| `agent.hostname` | agent.connect | `worker-1` |\n| `build.id` | scheduler, job.status_update | `build-12345` |\n\n### Filtering in Jaeger\n- `pipeline.name=demo` — all traces for that pipeline\n- `pipeline.counter=42` — a specific run\n- `error=true` — only failed spans\n- `operation=pipeline.trigger` — only trigger spans",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Attribute Reference",
      "type": "text"
    }
